headline.main: Maine's Biggest Dog Sled Race Celebrates 25th Anniversary
headline.print_headline: Maine's Biggest Dog Sled Race Celebrates 25th Anniversary

lead_paragraph: More than a dozen mushers departed Saturday amid a cacophony of barking dogs and cheering spectators for a 250-mile dash across the wilderness of northern Maine.
